name: Borders Woodworks
overview: Borders Woodworks, in Jacksonville, Florida, specializes in building and installing custom cabinets and custom furniture. We rely on high quality materials and quality craftsmanship to provide our clients with exceptional products that are tailored to their specific needs. Whether you are in need of new custom kitchen cabinets, a unique storage built-in, or entertainment built-in, Borders Woodworks will work closely with you to design and create cabinetry that will enhance your lifestyle and increase the value of your home.Borders Woodworks can be commissioned to design and build one of a kind furniture pieces that express the individuality of the Owner. Ranging from refined modern to rustic styles, we create top quality, functional pieces of art, by working with the Client to understand their tastes and expectations.
